A South Asian snack made with potatoes (<i>aloo</i> in Hindi/Urdu.) <i>Chaat</i> is a substantial snack or light meal characterized by a combination of sweet, spicy, sour and savory flavors and a mixture of textures ranging from crunchy to creamy. <i>Aloo chaat</i> might include spicy cooked potatoes in a cool yogurt sauce with a piquant sweet sauce and crunchy noodles on top.